# iosxe_crypto_ikev2_proposal (Data Source)

This data source can read the Crypto IKEv2 Proposal configuration.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "iosxe_crypto_ikev2_proposal" "example" {
  name = "PROPOSAL1"
}
```
